# Octet Policy SDK — CODEOWNERS
#
# Every change to policy data files (countries.json, states.json) and
# their sources.md requires review from a named compliance reviewer.
# Code changes follow normal engineering review.
#
# CODEOWNERS is advisory unless GitHub branch protection on `main` is
# configured to require code-owner review. That setting must be turned
# on — see README.md "For maintainers — branch protection".

# --- Default: any engineering reviewer ---
*                                       @octethacker

# --- Data files: compliance review required ---
policies/*/countries.json               @btf8000 @drew-octet
policies/*/states.json                  @btf8000 @drew-octet
policies/*/sources.md                   @btf8000 @drew-octet

# --- The OFAC predicate is highest-stakes; require both reviewers ---
policies/isOfacComprehensive/           @btf8000 @drew-octet
